== Development Team ==

=== Quintet Co., Ltd. ===

Robotrek was developed by Quintet, known for their action RPGs including:
* ActRaiser (1990)
* Soul Blazer (1992)
* Illusion of Gaia (1993)
* Terranigma (1995)

